  <Heading level={{ 1 }}>What is TR1X?</Heading>

  <p>
    TR1X is a lovingly rebuilt, enhanced version of the original Tomb Raider
    (1996) engine – a passion project that brings Lara's very first adventure
    into the modern age. It preserves the soul of the classic while adding
    dozens (and dozens!) of improvements, fixes, and optional tweaks. Whether
    you're a purist or an experimenter, TR1X lets you play your way.
  </p>
